title: Fallout 4 Far Harbor DLC-CODEX
description:
C O D E X
P R E S E N T S

Fallout 4 Far Harbor DLC (c) Bethesda Softworks

Release Date :  05/2016              Protection : Steam
Discs        :  1                    Genre      : RPG

A new case from Valentines Detective Agency leads you on  a  search
for a young woman and a secret colony  of synths.  Travel  off  the
coast of Maine to the mysterious island of Far Harbor, where higher
levels  of radiation  have created  a more  feral  world.  Navigate
through the growing conflict between the synths,  the  Children  of
Atom, and the local townspeople.

For more info go to : http://store.steampowered.com/app/435881/

- Run setup.exe and install DLC
- Copy crack from CODEX dir to installdir
- Play

This DLC requires:

Fallout.4-CODEX
+ Fallout.4.v1.4.Update-SKIDROW
+ Fallout.4.Update.v1.5-CODEX
